\[E=\begin{pmatrix}0&1&2&\cdots&L-1\\ 0&1&2&\cdots&L-1\\ \vdots&\vdots&\vdots&&\vdots\\ 0&1&2&\cdots&L-1\end{pmatrix}.\] (E.4)

